    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="P96-11">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>If the foolish call them 'flowers,'</l>
                    <l>Need the wiser tell?</l>
                    <l>If the savans 'classify' them,</l>
                    <l>It is just as well!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Those who read the Revelations</l>
                    <l>Must not criticise</l>
                    <l>Those who read the same edition</l>
                    <l>With beclouded eyes!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Could we stand with that old Moses</l>
                    <l>Canaan denied, </l>
                    <l>Scan, like him, the stately landscape</l>
                    <l>On the other side, </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Doubtless we should deem superfluous</l>
                    <l>Many sciences</l>
                    <l>Not pursued by learned angels</l>
                    <l>In scholastic skies!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Grant that we may stand,</l>
                    <l>Stars, amid profound Galaxies,</l>
                    <l>At that grand 'Right hand'!</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
        </body>
